  "name": "prescient-sdk",
  "readme": {
    "markdown": "# prescient-sdk\n\nPolyglot SDK for integrating with Prescient services. Generated from a single TypeScript source using [jsii](https://aws.github.io/jsii/).\n\n## Available packages\n\n| Language | Registry |\n| --- | --- |\n| TypeScript / JavaScript | npm |\n| Python | PyPI |\n| C# / .NET | NuGet |\n| Java | Maven Central |\n| Go | GitHub |\n\n## Development\n\nSee [JSII_MIGRATION_PLAN.md](../JSII_MIGRATION_PLAN.md) for the full migration plan.\n\n### Prerequisites\n\n- Node.js 18, 20, or 22\n- pnpm >= 11\n\n### Build\n\n```sh\npnpm install\npnpm run build\n```\n\n### Package (generate all language targets)\n\n```sh\npnpm run package\n```\n\n### Test\n\n```sh\npnpm test\n```\n"
  },
